    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You learn to magically ward yourself against attack and to turn an enemy's failed strike into good luck for yourself. When a creature makes an attack roll against you, you can take a Reaction to impose Disadvantage on that roll. If the attack misses you, your next attack roll against the creature has Advantage if you make it before the end of your next turn.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your Proficiency Bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a Long Rest. At 20th level in this class, you also regain all expended uses when you use your Eldritch Master feature.</p>",
